<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenido - EANSA</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body.home-hero {
            background-image: url('/images/hero.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            color: white;
        }
        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.60);
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .cta-box {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.40); 
            padding: 2.2rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
        }
    .logo-container { margin-left: -40px; }
    @media (max-width: 576px) { .logo-container { margin-left: 0; } }
        .logo-placeholder {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        .social-icons a { color: #fff; }
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .header-top { flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem; }
            .social-and-buttons { text-align: center; }
        }
        .footer-actions {
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .footer-actions .btn { opacity: 0.95; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="home-hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>

    <header class="container py-3 hero-content">
        <div class="d-flex header-top justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center logo-container">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo-placeholder me-3" />
                <div>
                    <h4 class="mb-0">EANSA - Sistema de mantenimiento</h4>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-end social-and-buttons">
                <div class="mb-2 social-icons">
                    <a href="#" class="me-2" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram fa-lg"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="me-2" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook fa-lg"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="me-2" aria-label="TikTok"><i class="fab fa-tiktok fa-lg"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container hero-content">
        <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height:65vh;">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6 text-center">
                <div class="cta-box mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">EANSA - Sistema de mantenimiento</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Mantén tus equipos en óptimas condiciones. Reporta incidencias, programa mantenimientos y controla historiales desde una sola plataforma.</p>

                    <p class="mb-4">Empieza ahora: crea una cuenta o inicia sesión para acceder al panel.</p>

                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-sm-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>Iniciar Sesión
                        </a>
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i>Registrarse
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="footer-actions hero-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-2 gap-sm-3">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">Ayuda</a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">Acerca de mí</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
